======== Private Message Alerts v5.2.1.00 ========
Created by Azumandias (azumandias _ at _ hotmail.com)
Original phorum coding by the Phorum Development Team (http://www.phorum.org)

========        Brief Description         ========
This module alerts a user to new private messages through on screen alerts.  The 
alerts will only be shown once per message (or group of messages if more than 
one message was received between visits). The alerts will give the user the 
option of going directly to the PM page.

========      Installation and Usage      ========
By default the private message alerts will appear on all pages and cannot be 
disabled.  The options available in the settings page are to not show alerts on 
PM pages and to allow the users to disable alerts for themselves.

